Well, now that we've gotten past that...<br>
<br>
Greetings. As many of you may have read, I am Xanath, former player of the character known as Xantess. I come before you today to inform you of the status of my account. As those of you who knew my character may know, several months ago, I disappeared. Xantess ceased to be online. The reasoning behind which is a number of things, mostly in relation to my real-life.<br>
<br>
As you know, I was an active EverQuest player. I quite frequently dueled, among other functions, such as newbie events and arena tournaments. Whether you feared or worshipped me, loved or hated me, odds are, a great deal of the server's population has, at one point or another, heard the name Xantess.<br>
<br>
It has come to my attention that my character will &quot;expire&quot; shortly. As in, all of the characters will be stripped of their equipment, and in an amount of time following, be removed from the server entirely. I do not wish for this to happen.<br>
<br>
I believe that I have found a person who is both willing and able to continue playing Xantess in the manner in which I would desire her to be played. Someone who is capable, patient, understanding, and creative, and who will no doubt fill the mold of the reputation I've built, while in time forging it into his own creation.<br>
<br>
That person is Noryko Angelcry, a long time friend of mine, who I have the utmost of trust and faith in. I ask of you all to treat him with the same respect as you would me, because though I myself will be unable to be in the game to provide pleasure and entertainment, Noryko will be.<br>
<br>
It is my opinion that though I do not generally condone or sanction the transfer or selling of accounts, in this case, it will be my legacy to the Druzzil Ro community. Though my decision may not be &quot;right&quot; in accordance to the game's End-user Licensing Agreement, I believe that my decision will be a helpful and productive one, for the entire community.<br>
<br>
Once again, you shall experience kindness, enjoyment, and amusement in the presence of the character known as Xantess.<br>
<br>
Thank you for your time.<br>
<br>
<br>
